Package: binsegment
Type: Package
Title: Binary Segmentation Trees
Version: 0.5.0
Author: Felipe Gerard
Maintainer: Felipe Gerard <felipegerard@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides semi-automatic tools for producing client segmentations. It is based on the premise that a good segmentation should both improve the predictive power of a score (Gini Index) but also make sense for business.
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    optimbucket
LazyData: TRUE
